Question: Explain to your grandmother how to use her smartphone to find new restaurant in her area.
Answer:
well, first, open your phone, find the application called map, and tabed it to open the application. you will see your location and the map around you. second, you will see a box at the top and there is a mirror near by. it is the search box, type restaurants in the box and press enter. then it will show all the restaurants around you.